/// ClassMethodsOnly — Object subclass exposing only class-side methods
/// (FFI-namespace pattern). Class-shape flavour: class-methods-only class.
Object subclass: ClassMethodsOnly

  class identity: x => x

  class greeting -> String => "hi"

  class doubled: n => n * 2
